race.comment: IL CIELO (2) was ridden with confidence by the claimer last time, sitting second and drawing right away to score. Could be ridden with cover this time from a lower draw but now back in form can go close again. TAXING (7) is better than last couple suggest, the latest racing on speed before fading in a richer assignment at Cranbourne. Gets chance to bounce back. DIVINE TURF (8) hasn't been far away from a win and looks well placed here. Blinkers added and will be doing best work late. SEEYOU RAIDER (1) has been freshened since racing on speed and fading last time. Better than that and looks the one to take up the running here. ALGADON STORM (13) has been ticking along well without winning and is drawn for a soft run.
